            <div type="a">
                <column>3</column>
                <head>Augusta a Bell County</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer>"It has more Bell voters than any county.... It has more persons by the
                    name of Bell, we venture to say, than any county in the State, all of whom, we
                    suppose, will be related to the President if Bell should be elected.... It has
                    more ladies who are entitled to be considered belles than any county in the good
                    'Old Commonwealth.'"</trailer>
                <names/>
                <summary>Spectator lists reasons why Augusta is the strongest Bell county in the
                    state.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
